1_1H9R6W9QWUpYiJkLyAsFXmXhAV7HEqoHtN.body: It is game written by me. :-] Assembler. Win32api. Works perfectly at WinXP32. Name is Hookworms. It is like "Snake" or "Piton" games but it is multiplayer on one computer. Up to 8 players can struggle. There are two game modes. Classical - you die, you wait for one player to survive, so only survivor is winner of a round. Deathmatch - nonstop game, you die, you respawn instantly. Game is very fun if you have other 3-4 human players and some usb-keyboard/joystics. I think that is enough for test comment.
